"\"<p data-start=\\\"214\\\" data-end=\\\"435\\\">Safety starts with knowledge. <em data-start=\\\"244\\\" data-end=\\\"266\\\">Hazard Communication<\/em> empowers employees and leaders to understand <strong data-start=\\\"312\\\" data-end=\\\"350\\\">Material Safety Data Sheets (MSDS)<\/strong>, warning labels, and workplace hazards to prevent accidents and ensure compliance.<br><br><\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"437\\\" data-end=\\\"622\\\">This session is especially designed for those working in <strong data-start=\\\"494\\\" data-end=\\\"552\\\">manufacturing, warehouses, engineering and maintenance<\/strong>, as well as <strong data-start=\\\"565\\\" data-end=\\\"619\\\">housekeeping teams in hotels, malls, and companies<\/strong>.<\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"624\\\" data-end=\\\"653\\\">Participants will learn to:<br><br><\/p>\\n<ul data-start=\\\"654\\\" data-end=\\\"878\\\">\\n<li data-start=\\\"654\\\" data-end=\\\"714\\\">\\n<p data-start=\\\"656\\\" data-end=\\\"714\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"656\\\" data-end=\\\"683\\\">Read and interpret MSDS<\/strong> for chemicals and materials.<\/p>\\n<\/li>\\n<li data-start=\\\"715\\\" data-end=\\\"782\\\">\\n<p data-start=\\\"717\\\" data-end=\\\"782\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"717\\\" data-end=\\\"746\\\">Understand warning labels<\/strong> and the precautions they require.<\/p>\\n<\/li>\\n<li data-start=\\\"783\\\" data-end=\\\"878\\\">\\n<p data-start=\\\"785\\\" data-end=\\\"878\\\">Implement <strong data-start=\\\"795\\\" data-end=\\\"839\\\">effective hazard communication practices<\/strong> to promote a safer work environment.<br><br><\/p>\\n<\/li>\\n<\/ul>\\n<p data-start=\\\"880\\\" data-end=\\\"1040\\\">Through practical examples and real-life scenarios, this workshop helps organizations <strong data-start=\\\"966\\\" data-end=\\\"1037\\\">create a culture of safety, awareness, and informed decision-making<\/strong>.<\/p>\""